"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-21-olympic-defector-responds-critics-faces-two-year-ban-team-gb-switch-21461402\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Three-timeOlympicmedalist Matthew Richardsonhas defended his decision to switch from Australia toTeam GBdespite facing the potential of a two-year ban from competing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 85, \"end\": 94, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.8978675838487712, \"rank\": 0.11289263366988822, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cycling star won silvers in the individual sprint and keirin as well as bronze in the team sprint at theParisOlympics but shocked teammates shortly after the Games whenannouncing his intention to switch nationalityand ride for Great Britain going forward.\", \"from\": 168, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.648789010064479e-41, \"text\": \"keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999403253259, \"rank\": 3.3438519785611076e-08, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson was born in Maidstone, England and moved toAustraliaat the age of nine but has faced huge criticism for the decision, most notably from former Commonwealth champion Katherine Bates.\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9998525801841412, \"rank\": 0.00014744155134383772, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.779142016234284, \"rank\": 0.21516710335728534, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999996705355, \"rank\": 3.1307856753282206e-10, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Bates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katherine Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Bates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is a lot of people who just can not believe it and some who are feeling, personally, quite let down because they were blindsided by it,' Bates said.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"score\": 0.9998685039077222, \"rank\": 0.00013116239773464626, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Others who are feeling a little bit ripped off because supporting him over the years has come at the direct cost of supporting other athletes.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think the tie to your country is very strong but, in saying that, if there is that tie, then I am not really sure why he would not have made this leap years ago.'\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Richardson, who is in a relationship with Team GB cycling star Emma Finucane, has now addressed his controversial and said he feels no remorse over the decision.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9998525801841412, \"rank\": 0.00014744155134383772, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9945452166575438, \"rank\": 0.005056478438465435, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"score\": 0.9995796654043068, \"rank\": 0.00026754067537522767, \"text\": \"Emma\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I obviously understood that there would be a bit of bitterness around this decision, but at the end of the day it's my career and it's my life,' he toldABC News.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Everyone's entitled to their opinion.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's up to me whether I want to listen to it or not, and I have obviously chosen not to.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a free world, and they can do and say what they like.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am happy with the decision I have made.'\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding directing to Bates' suggestion that Australian cycling had been 'ripped off' by his departure, the 25-year-old said: 'The investment that was put into me over the last few years in Australian cycling, I feel like I made a good return on that investment, winning two silver medals and a bronze medal at the Olympic Games for Australia.'\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1685, \"end\": 1690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"score\": 0.9998685039077222, \"rank\": 0.00013116239773464626, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\"}, {\"begin\": 1708, \"end\": 1718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.999431249767416, \"rank\": 0.0005572162671989104, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1853, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.999431249767416, \"rank\": 0.0005572162671989104, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1996, \"end\": 2005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.8978675838487712, \"rank\": 0.11289263366988822, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson will not be able to compete at the next World Championships in October following the switch but the cyclist could yet be hit with further punishment by his former employers after AusCycling chief Jesse Korf confirmed they may seek to impose a two-year non-competition ban on Richardson.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2009, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9998525801841412, \"rank\": 0.00014744155134383772, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AusCycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\"}, {\"begin\": 2295, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9998525801841412, \"rank\": 0.00014744155134383772, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is disappointment around the decision and the process and not knowing around Matt's circumstances,' Korf, AusCycling's executive general manager of performance, said  'He will not compete at the upcoming World Championships [in October].\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AusCycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But the non-competition duration and clauses, that is being interrogated and looked into at the moment together with the UCI (Union Cycliste Internationale) and ASC (Australian Sports Commission).\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2676, \"end\": 2679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999999997853593, \"rank\": 2.1217198095024667e-10, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 2716, \"end\": 2719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\", \"score\": 0.963087119856628, \"rank\": 0.03821396833207656, \"text\": \"ASC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\"}, {\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Sports Commission\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That is something that we would have to discuss internally because we obviously have a big say in that and we need to review that.'\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Any decision to impose a two-year ban lies with the UCI and not AusCycling.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2939, \"end\": 2942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999999997853593, \"rank\": 2.1217198095024667e-10, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Missing big international competitions is not obviously ideal, but I think that's why I had to do it when I did it, so I missed the least amount of them possible,' Richardson said.\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9998525801841412, \"rank\": 0.00014744155134383772, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3197, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympics are relentless and exhausting, but I would have crawled onto the pitch to play  ArrowMORE:Team GB athletes to look out for at the Paralympics as Thomas Young and Claire Taggart aim to clinch gold medals  ArrowMORE:The bizarre tattoo rule that could get Paralympians banned from Paris Games  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3433, \"end\": 3445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Yonge\", \"score\": 0.9289345702379647, \"rank\": 0.075884352499845, \"text\": \"Thomas Young\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Yonge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Yonge\"}, {\"begin\": 3450, \"end\": 3464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Taggart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Claire Taggart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Taggart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Taggart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3823, \"to\": 3995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3885, \"end\": 3891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3997, \"to\": 4128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4189, \"entities\": []}]}"